{"tid":1402033,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"重新檢視 - 勇武同和理非進化步伐","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:30:40.000Z","uid":93137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dbeee2c10ea70122f8eb5e5647da7baf9c16f60d","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"勇武 - <br />\n每次行動都有升級，但已經到樽頸。<br />\n開始迷失方向，除左即時戰略更需要賽後檢討，去支持前線信心。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為：要對付速龍襲擊，就係用自殺式反撲。<br />\n我知會有好大爭議，邊個肯做？<br />\n原諒我鍵盤戰士冷氣軍師，係個mon面前講不負責任說話。<br />\n與其每次比班狗一晚捉幾十人，不如用幾十人去反撲班狗，咁樣先可以突破到樽頸狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 - <br />\n200萬大遊行、機場和平集會、公務員集會等等都比到好大信息比公眾。<br />\n我地必需要認同，香港大部分市民都係和理非，佢地嘅支持係超級重要。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為：要不斷搞大遊行，最理想係每次都有百萬計嘅市民上街，令到社會持續有聲音。我明白太過理想，但當日你又點估到會有200萬人行岀黎呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都需要進化，依加戰力再消耗落去，好快就沉船，一沉不起。"},{"pid":"1fc2ff32826b3374c2a63db25f0172b486985241","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50b56c1c9ec167c40d29714380c4b682c1727d76","tid":1402033,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"[建議]關於罷買！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7800a165e499534cd6388f3174e68885f03b582","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:33:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"802ab8a74426bc4fa92a9219feccedd11dee6cf0","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"899891197ed90e57623e5342a75a01e0550f45f5","tid":1402033,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8c087c81c3b47b24be98c32c27239726e1559b1","tid":1402033,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明顯有狗扮示威者<br />\n引你地留低<br />\n不戀戰 <br />\n不分化   只是各自轉場<br />\nbe water<br />\nhit n run!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7b2a12a9662b50bcbd8c1cd5e9c39c7af3de46c","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f47a5dedc7a58de06290bd6c6ecf2c6359414fd0","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac9c04ce12a8408eaa3672b46620fc71e34c8998","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1187bea398b044548a5168e9610a56551aaab20a","tid":1402033,"uid":199456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"個人睇法<br />\n勇武必須要保命 先可以有下一次<br />\n和理非必須要多出黎 先可以支持勇武<br />\n<br />\n兩者都要 流水式 多戰線 忌長時間守"},{"pid":"de3ed0b96e3ff6625f658054263dbf63974880e4","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1187bea398b044548a5168e9610a56551aaab20a","tid":1402033,"uid":199456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"個人睇法<br />\n勇武必須要保命 先可以有下一次<br />\n和理非必須要多出黎 先可以支持勇武<br />\n<br />\n兩者都要 流水式 多戰線 忌長時間守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"如果真係傾向保命，咁一定要制訂轉場方式。否則只會重蹈覆轍。"},{"pid":"7deff896ded0b7f43865eb7645f71dc5b4096dfc","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb09594e83897a19a440366d53db4ac02ce33f94","tid":1402033,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"388889d2719f4d8178f8a